			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1645622">
									

<p>Hey! I was thinking to do that in a meta tale. A self insert character who is aware that even his own existence is merely a representation of the author of the tale.</p>
<p>&quot;You have to understand that i'm here, but not in a way that you could see clearly. I'm guiding every action in this moment&#8230;</p>
<p>I'm not a reality bender, they shift the reality with their minds. I create the reality, not with my mind but the word.</p>
<p>Yes, the word, and letters, sentences, phrases, etc etc etc. Didn't you ever read the bible? God created the universe with his word&#8230;.&quot;</p>
<p>Ok, my brainstorm stopped here, but you get the point c:.</p>

